8. Functional Requirements
8.1 AI Image Generation Flow

User Flow:

User writes a prompt (e.g., “Metallic organic texture in blue and silver”)

Clicks “Generate”

Frontend sends prompt to backend

Backend calls OpenAI Image Generation API

Image is returned

Image is previewed in the browser

8.2 Send to Bag Flow

User clicks “Send to Bag”

Frontend sends image (base64 or URL) to Node.js backend

Backend forwards image to Raspberry Pi

Raspberry Pi renders image on HDMI screen

Must occur in real time.

8.3 LED Control

User can:

Select RGB color

Optionally adjust brightness

Flow:

Frontend → Backend → Raspberry Pi → GPIO → LED strip

8.4 Servo Activation

User clicks activation control.

Flow:

Frontend → Backend → Raspberry Pi → GPIO → Servo movement

Movement sequence is predefined and limited.

